data.description: A new Home in time for the Holidays! Settle into this beautiful home nestled in an intimate and well-maintained subdivision in Decatur.  This home is spacious with a perfect flow for entertaining or just for your family to relax in!  Relax in the family room with ample space for sectional seating and a game table area! Behind the French doors off the family room, you’ll find the perfect space for a den or a home office. The Dining room is directly off the kitchen allowing for ease in dinner service.  The kitchen has space for a dining table, ample cabinets and two prep areas… and it opens to the back deck, perfect for those summer barbeques. Next you will find two staircases, one from the family room and the other from the kitchen to access the 2nd floor. The bedrooms on this level are equally as spacious with two of the secondary bedrooms as spacious as a Master complete with walk in closets!  The laundry room is conveniently located on this level as well. You’ll find the location of the home while peaceful and in a neighboring setting, accessible to supermarkets, restaurants and two malls!  The best of both worlds! Bring your clients to their forever home in Decatur.
